overview:
Jenny Nedanovski, founder of Milkshake-factory.com, is an innovative entrepreneur and your dedicated marketing expert.

Jenny Nedanovski is an independent Marketing Consultant with many years of experience working in Technical and Managerial positions.

After many years working in various industries, Jenny Nedanovski understands both technology and business practice and can provide advice on how to create optimal marketing solutions for your business.

Whether in government, agency, large corporation, private organisation or small business, Jenny is ready to provide you with ‘Complete Marketing Solutions’ on services and product requirements.
